sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Browser
    participant RP as Reverse Proxy
    participant BE as Backend
    participant ML as ML Service
    participant P as Postgres Primary
    participant A as Audit Postgres
    participant S as MinIO/Storage

    U->>RP: POST /api/cases/{id}/run
    RP->>BE: Forward API request
    BE->>P: Write inference_run status=RUNNING
    BE->>A: Insert audit_event(INFERENCE_STARTED)
    BE->>ML: POST /infer {artifact references}
    ML->>S: Read input artifacts
    ML-->>BE: Inference result metadata
    BE->>P: Persist findings/reports/artifacts metadata
    BE->>A: Insert audit_event(INFERENCE_COMPLETED)
    BE-->>RP: 200 response
    RP-->>U: API response
